      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 1:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". David must have erected a new altar for sacrifice at Jerusalem ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 16:1",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The sacrifices commanded by the Law were, it appears, offered at the former place; at the latter were offered voluntary additional sacrifices.",
